snippet.title: Nightmare Fuel - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download for free now: https://fatumblack.itch.io/nightmarefuel
Developer: Fatum Black / Publisher: Zero7even

Elvira has violated her mother's main injunction 'not to mix alcohol with drugs' and is about to die at the underground techno rave. Well-built Pink Rabbit appears unexpectedly and makes a strange proposal (refusal is not accepted). Now, the girl must save the Pink Kingdom, taste cucumber pizza and, who knows, deal with the cockroaches in her mind.
